<p>Kazan Arena stadium opens it's doors to all the football enthusiasts, citizens and guests of Kazan! Have a walk around the stadium and learn the history of it's construction, take a seat at the players bench and get a look of their changing rooms, enjoy a stroll around the tribunes. </p>
<p>Tours can be paid for by cash at the ticket windows at the stadium or by a debit/credit card. Group tours inquiries have to be arranged at least 3 days before the date of the tour. We can accept groups with up to 30 members in one group. Special offers for the tour operators. </p>
